    public abstract class AbstractGenericService<P extends Provider,M extends Manager>
extends AbstractService
    An abstract extension of AbstractService class holding Provider and Manager instances. This skeleton implementation provides an abstract builder mechanism to construct instances of extended classes.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
